I want to help people. I want to work with kids who have been hurt. I want to help families. I think social work is the right job for me.

I want to help in the Division of Family and Children Services. This group helps kids who have been hurt. They help families too. 

I have good values. I want to help others. I am fair. I am honest. I want to learn and grow as a worker. These values are important to me.

I always wanted to help people. In high school and college, I saw people who had problems. Some people tried to hide from their problems. Some people used bad ways to deal with their problems. I saw things that made me want to help.

I took classes in psychology.  I wanted to help people but I did not know how. After I finished school, I took a break. One day, I met a boy. He was scared. He was running away from his parents. They were hurting him. I wanted to help. I talked to the police.

The police asked me to talk to the parents. They said there was nothing they could do. I talked to the parents. They were nervous. They did not want to admit they were hurting their son. 

After this, I knew I wanted to be a social worker. I want to help kids like this boy.

Social workers help people who are treated unfairly. We say that everyone is important. But sometimes we are not fair. 

I believe in treating everyone fairly. In high school and college, I fought for fairness. I showed people that I was different. I joined a group that helped people who are gay, straight, or bisexual. I fought against racism and discrimination. I will continue to fight for fairness.

This paper looks at two ways to understand sleep problems: the biological model and the sociocultural model. The biological model looks at sleep problems as caused by genes and medical things. The sociocultural model looks at how things like where a person lives, their family, and their money affect their sleep. This paper looks at studies that show how these models work. It also talks about the good and bad parts of each study.

Sleep problems can be caused by many things. They can be a main problem, or they can be caused by another problem like a mental health problem. Sleep problems can also be caused by medicine or being sick.

There are many types of sleep problems. Some common ones are trouble falling asleep, trouble staying asleep, and sleepwalking. Sleep problems can be caused by things like stress, anxiety, and depression.

This paper looks at insomnia, which is trouble falling asleep, and how it is related to the biological and sociocultural models.

One study looked at how genes affect sleep. Scientists studied mice and found that certain genes control how much a mouse sleeps. They also found that a medicine that affects these genes can help mice sleep better. This shows that genes can play a big role in how well we sleep.

Another study looked at how culture affects sleep. Scientists studied people from different cultures and found that people from different cultures sleep for different amounts of time. They also found that people from different cultures have different sleep habits. This shows that culture can also play a big role in how well we sleep.

This paper talk about three things about Central Auditory Processing Disorder (CAPD). First, it give a short meaning of the disorder. Next, it talk about how to know if a person has CAPD. Finally, it give ideas for teachers to help a student with CAPD in a normal classroom. 

Central Auditory Processing Disorder (CAPD), or Auditory Processing Disorder (APD), is when the brain has trouble using sound.  The brain can hear sound, but it can not use the sound well. A person with CAPD can hear like other people, but their brain does not understand sound well. The part of the brain that makes sense of sound does not work like it should.

People first talk about this problem in the 1950s. They called it “auditory imperception.” Doctors started to figure out how to test for it in the 1960s. In 1977, a big meeting help people learn more about CAPD. 

CAPD can show up in many ways. A person with CAPD may not hear sound well in space. They may have trouble hearing two sounds at the same time. They may not hear patterns in sound. They may not understand changes in a person’s voice. One sound may block another sound. They may not understand the order of sounds.

To know if a person has CAPD, doctors have to test them. They watch how the person listens and give them tests. They use many different tests. There is no one test that is perfect. There is no known reason why people get CAPD.

Twelfth Night show us that disguise can help people hide. But it can also make people lose who they are. It is hard to stop hiding. People may be angry if they find out they were tricked.

It is hard for people to change genders. Why do people want to be someone else? In the play, Viola needs to be a man to stay safe. She says, "I will bring you to a captain in this town/Where lie my maiden weeds, by whose gentle help/ I was preserved to serve this noble count…”  

Being a man helps Viola, but it also makes it hard for her to be friends with other women. It is even harder when Olivia falls in love with Viola. Olivia says, "Whither, my lord? Cesario, husband, stay.” Viola also has feelings for Orsino. He says, "Boy, thou hast said to me a thousand times/Thou never shouldst love woman like to me.”

Twelfth Night shows us that hiding can help people feel things. Olivia and Orsino may have feelings they do not know about. 

Olivia likes Cesario. Does she like men or women? Maybe she is just like people in that time who judge people by how they look. She falls in love with Sebastian when he arrives. She calls Viola her sister.

German rule in Africa was hard. It was mean to the people who lived there. This is true for the Ovaherero and Nama people in German South West Africa. The German government did bad things to them.  But German rule was not all bad.  

The German government gave education to some Africans in some parts of Africa. This is true for German East Africa (now called Tanganyika). Many Africans were able to read and write there.  Other places, like Kamerun, also had good schools. South West Africa was different. 

The German government did not help with education there. They let churches teach the Africans. The churches did not have much money or help. The German government did help white people learn. They made schools for white children. They also helped churches teach white children.

This made a big difference in South West Africa. Many Africans could not read or write there. Other places had more educated Africans. This paper looks at why this was. What made South West Africa so different?  

There are many books about education in Africa when Germany ruled it. Many of these books are in German. They were written a long time ago. The first books just described the schools. Later books looked at all the German colonies. They saw that the schools were different in each place. One book looked at South West Africa and East Africa. 

South West Africa was not very hot or cold.  Many white people lived there. There were more white people in South West Africa than in any other place where Germany ruled.

Popular music has many kinds. It is hard to list all of them.  Many kinds, like rap, rock, country, jazz, and folk, have many smaller kinds. Heavy metal rock is one kind that has become very big. It is popular because it shows many feelings. The feelings are often sad or dark. Heavy metal has many smaller kinds too. People made new kinds of heavy metal soon after it started.

Today, there are so many kinds of heavy metal, it is hard to say what heavy metal is. It has taken ideas from other kinds of music, but it started somewhere. To understand heavy metal today, we must understand how it started.

Heavy metal is a movement, not just a kind of music. It is about being loud and strong. Heavy metal music has lots of bass and drums. The musicians are very good. It is also a movement that uses drugs. In the 1970s, people used many drugs. This made the music strange and different. Heavy metal is dark and strong. This is new for popular music. Many kinds of music do not show dark feelings. 

Heavy metal music also uses ideas from the Romantic period. This period was known for its dark and strong feelings. Here are some words from a metal song:

(Byrne)

These words show the dark side of the Beatles. The song is about drugs. Some people say this song is one of the first heavy metal songs. The Beatles wanted to be as loud and strong as the Rolling Stones.

Henri Rousseau was a painter. Many years ago, he made a painting called "The Dream." This painting shows a woman in a dream. It also shows the artist's dreams. 

Rousseau wanted to be a good painter. He wanted other people to like his art. But he also wanted to be different. This made him sad. 

Rousseau was born a long time ago in France. He did not go to art school. He worked for the government for many years. He was sad because his wife and many children died. He started to paint to make himself happy.

Rousseau wanted to be famous. Many other artists were famous. Rousseau wanted to be like them. He wanted to paint like them. He knew he was different, but he wanted to be accepted.

One art expert said that Rousseau wanted to paint in a normal way so people would like him. This is different from another artist, Matisse. Matisse wanted to paint in a new way.

Many person think that truth and beauty are close. I agree. John Keats said, “Beauty is truth, truth beauty." We learn many things in school and from life. But we know truth and beauty in a different way. We do not need to be taught them.

Truth and beauty try to show us things. They do not tell us what to do. We study art and morals to know why things are good or bad. We try to explain why a painting is beautiful or why an action is right.

We can talk about art and morals, but we can not explain them fully. We can talk about a painting, like Mona Lisa, and say things about its colors and shapes. But these things do not say why it is good art.

When we like a book or painting, we often say, "There is something about it." We can not explain it. Art and morals can not be fully described. Flannery O'Connor said, "A story is a way to say something that can not be said any other way."

No matter how much we talk about art, there is still something more. Ethics is like this too. Wittgenstein said, "Ethics can not be said. Ethics is bigger than words." I think this "something" is the best part of art and morals. It is why they are so important.

We feel art and morals deeply. They are important parts of our lives. This is especially true for literature.  McKean said, "Literature is different from other arts because it has morals. Values are important in life, and literature shows us those values."

Germany is a strong country. It has one culture. The culture is all over Germany. It starts in München near the mountains. It goes to Kiel by the sea. The culture is the same in Köln on the Rhine River and in Dresden on the Elbe River. Germany has a special culture. This is because it came from many different tribes.

The name Germany comes from Germania. Germania is the old name for Germany. People do not know for sure where the name came from. One man named Tacitus said the name came from a tribe called the Tungrians. They were German people. Before they crossed the Rhine River, they fought the Gaulish people. Julius Caesar first used the word “Germanus.” He used it in his books about the Gallic Wars. He fought the Gauls and the German tribes. He used the word to show the difference between the Gauls and the Germans. Some people think the word came from the Gauls. They may have used it to talk about their neighbors.  Caesar wrote in his books: “Germans, who dwell beyond the Rhine, with whom they (The Gauls) are continually waging war.....They contend with the Germans in almost daily battles.”

Another writer, Tacitus, said that the Germans were the first people in the land. He said they did not mix with other people. He said, “I should regard (The Germans) as aboriginal, and not mixed at all with other races through immigration or intercourse. For, in former times it was not by land but on shipboard that those who sought to emigrate would arrive.......Who would leave Asia, or Africa, for Italy for Germany, with its wild country, its inclement skies, its sullen manners and aspect, unless indeed it were his home?”

The Romans did not want to live in Germania. They sent people to get goods from Germania. They also sent armies to fight the German tribes. But mostly, they went back to their own empire. The German tribes lived on the borders of the Roman Empire. They traded goods and fought for the Romans in their army.

I look down.  I see the thing in front of me.  My mind is quiet.  I see the thing.  My mind goes over the thing.  My mind does not feel any thing for the thing.

A man who makes art told me to buy a book.  The book is called  *The New Drawing on the Right Side of the Brain*.  I want to learn to make art.  I want to learn since I was six years old.  The book teaches you how to see.  It teaches you about lines.  One thing the book says is to put a box around a thing.  This makes the thing easy to see.  

I look at the thing.  The thing is hard to see.  I see a bowl of fruit.  It is on a table.  The table is in a room.  The room is big.

Picasso made art with blue.  Monet liked green.  Italian artists liked many colors.

I want to make art.  This is my art.  I call it “Work in Brown.”

I take a thing to make art.  I hold it in my hand.  I move my hand.  My mind tells my hand what to do.  This is the time to make art.

Water moves.  It is smooth.  It is clear.  Pieces of the thing fall off. They go to the bottom.  My hand moves.  My hand is fast.  My hand hits the thing again.  It does not move.

I have a mop.  I stand up.  I tie a tie.  It is green.  It is tight.  I look at the thing.  It is bad.

I flush the water.  I look at the thing.  It does not move.

I take paper.  I put it around the thing.

I stand up.  I bend down.  I put my hand in the water.

Teen people die in car crashes. Many things make this a big problem for young drivers. The National Institutes of Health say young people's brains are not ready for driving. They also have little experience. This leads to more crashes, rollovers, speeding, and driving off the road.
Young people also drive worse when their friends ride with them. This is true because young people often drive with their friends. A study in Southern California showed that the more young people are in a car, the more crashes happen. 

States try to make driving safer for teens. They give out special driver's licenses that limit driving time and the number of passengers. But these licenses are only a small help. The real problem is that young drivers are not ready for the risks of driving. A doctor named Marvin Zuckerman says 18 is too young to get a full license. He says young people like to take risks.

We should wait longer before young people can drive. We need to wait until they are older and take fewer risks. If we do not, more young people will die in crashes. Many more young drivers will be on the road soon.  

We can make driving safer. Schools can teach young people about driving. But no one under 18 should drive a car. They can get a special permit before they get a full license. They also need to practice driving with an adult.

The number of practice hours should be the same in every state. Right now, states have different rules.  National rules would help everyone.

I look at films from the Library of Congress. I see many old Edison films. I look at fifteen trick films from 1895 to 1901. These films use tricks to show things that are not real. My work looks at how these films use tricks. I also look at some films that are different.

Trick films from this time are made inside a box. The camera does not move. The films are long shots, not close shots. This is like theater. The audience sees the whole stage. Actors move side to side. They do not move towards or away from the camera.

For example, in the film "Uncle Josh in a Spooky Hotel" (1900), actors move back and forth. The camera does not follow them.

Most trick films are short. They are about one minute long. They show magic tricks. They do not have a long story.

A trick film may look like one shot. But, it can be many shots put together. In the film "The Execution of Mary, Queen of Scots" (1895), the shot of Mary's head is made with many shots.

John Taylor was from Carolina. He liked the idea of people having freedom. He was a farmer. This made him think about how to make the government good. He liked the idea of farmers being able to make their own rules. John Taylor thought the United States was new. This was good. It could make a good system for people to rule themselves. He believed people have rights. These rights are important. If one right is lost, then all rights are in danger. These rights should be safe from the government. John Taylor said that in the past, strong people took what they wanted. He wanted a better system. He believed the government should help people be good and stop them from being bad. He thought people are good and bad. The government should help the good and stop the bad.

John Taylor wanted the government to be small. He wanted the government to only do what the Constitution said. He thought a big government could be dangerous. He also thought that the Constitution should be read carefully. It should not be read too simply. He thought the Declaration of Independence was more important. It said the United States was made up of states that could rule themselves.

Figure 17 shows a big drop in commuter log reports in the third month of the project. This was sad. We do not know why this happened.  

Winter came to the New England school. Fewer people rode bikes or walked to school. This may explain some of the drop. December is the end of the fall school year. Students are busy with schoolwork and grades. They may not have filled out the log reports. December is also a busy time for holidays. Students and teachers have a long break. They do not need to go to school.

Classes start again in January. This may also explain why there were few reports in January. But this does not explain why there were few reports in February.

It is normal for projects to start with lots of energy. Then, the energy may go down. To stop this, we had the Carpool Challenge Week in March. This helped bring back more reports.

One problem was keeping people interested. People like to drive their cars. This is common in our culture. We need to give people reasons to use other ways to get to school. We gave out prizes like gift cards to restaurants and stores. It would be interesting to see if bigger prizes, like a bike or a car, would help more people join.  

We did not change the prizes during the project. If we gave bigger prizes later, more people might have joined. Gift cards were good at first, but bigger prizes later might have been better.

An ETF is a way to own many stocks at once. It is like a stock, but it owns other things, like many stocks or things that are not stocks. ETFs are like a group of stocks. You can buy or sell them on a big stock market.

ETFs are good because they are less expensive than other groups of stocks. They also let you buy or sell small parts of them.

But, you have to pay a small fee each time you buy or sell an ETF. ETFs have many different kinds. It is good to check if an ETF really does what it says.

For this work, we will look at one ETF called IHF. We will look at its biggest parts. These parts make up most of the ETF. We will see if these parts are as good as the whole ETF.

We will also see if there are better ways to own these parts. This would mean buying them one by one, not in an ETF. We will see if this is better for making money.

To do this, we will look at how much money the parts make. We will also look at how much they go up and down in price. We will see if the parts are better than the whole ETF.

Dream-Land is one of Edgar Allan Poe's good poems. In "Dream-Land", Poe uses the word "Thulé". Poe learned this word from Virgil. Virgil used the word for an island. Greeks thought this island was far away. Poe also liked German writers.  

One writer was Goethe. A book about Poe says Poe liked Goethe's work. The book says Poe copied Goethe's poem.

Goethe wrote a famous play called "Faust".  It has two parts. "Faust" is about a man who makes a deal with the devil. In part two, there is a short poem called "The King of Thulé". The king's wife dies. He is sad. He drinks too much. He wants to die. He throws a cup into the sea and dies.

The king in "The King of Thulé" is sad. Poe's king in "Dream-Land" is also sad. Maybe Poe was thinking about his own sadness.  Poe read "Faust" before he wrote about Thulé.

Poe used the word "Thulé" twice in his writing. He used it in "Dream-Land" at the end of the poem. "The King of Thulé" and "Dream-Land" are similar.  

Poe's poem is like a copy of Goethe's poem. Poe's speaker is sad. He sees dark things. He is alone. This is like Goethe's poem. 

Goethe was a good writer. Poe knew Goethe's work.

A customer in California fell in a store. The customer was hurt.  The store had a spill of applesauce. The store worker knew about the spill. The worker did not clean it up. Can the customer get money from the store?

A judge will look at the case carefully. To get extra money, the customer must show that the worker did bad things on purpose. The customer must show that the worker knew the spill was dangerous and did not care. 

The customer can say that the worker knew spills were dangerous. Other people had fallen before. The worker still did not clean the spill. 

This case is about a worker named Martin. He was at dinner break. He did not want to clean the spill. A worker named Rich told Martin about the spill.  Martin said he did not have time. Another worker, Mary, told Martin about the spill. Martin said the same thing.

Jennifer Palmer fell and hurt her back. She is suing the store for money. The store may ask the judge to throw out the case.

In California, a customer can get extra money if the store worker acted badly. The worker must have been mean, dishonest, or acted on purpose to hurt someone. The worker must have known the spill was dangerous and did not care.

Four years ago, I took a class about Islam. We talked about if Islam is bad. This is still a big question today. After 9/11, news showed Islam in a bad way. Now, it shows Islam in a good way. We could not have had a president named Barack Obama with a Muslim family in 2001.

Muhammad’s story is interesting. I thought he forced people to be Muslim. He took over tribes and made them Muslim. But his story says he was a good man. People liked him and became Muslim.

Jesus and Muhammad did similar things. Muhammad made food appear for many people. This makes Muhammad seem like a good man. It is not good because it makes Jesus seem less important.

The book has stories about people becoming Muslim. But these stories come from other people. This is not good proof.

I do not like that the book makes Muhammad seem like a good man. History says he was not good. I wonder if Muslims know the real story about Muhammad.

Jesus teach many good things.  People who follow Jesus start new religion call Christian. Many people want to know more about Jesus.  

People change religion over time.  World change fast now.  Some people like old ways.  Other people want new ideas.  Many people want to know more about what Jesus really teach.


Many years from now, people will study about Jesus more. They want to know what he really said. They want to know what his religion was really about.  People will go back to old ways.  Christianity will become more like it was when Jesus live. People will read what Jesus said and follow his ideas.

This will happen in America and Europe.  Many people will follow Jesus ideas.   Churches will be strong.  They will help people follow Jesus.  Many people will believe the same things.   They will do the same things.

History show us that things can change.  People can change.  A long time ago, people did bad things to Christians.  But then people change.  Now, many Christians are leaders.  

In the future, Christianity will change again.  People will read what Jesus said in a new way.  They will see the meaning of his words.

I think "The Jungle" shows that people can be very selfish. They want good things for themself. They do not care about people who are not as lucky. "The Jungle" shows this in many ways. The men who own the big factories only want to make more money. They do not care if people get hurt. Upton Sinclair writes, "The line of the buildings stood clear-cut and black against the sky; here and there out of the mass rose the great chimneys, with the river of smoke streaming away to the end of the world". Sinclair shows how bad the pollution is. The owners do not care about people or animals. They do not care about the smoke from the factories or the waste from the animals.

The owners do not care about the workers. They want to make more money. Sinclair writes, "So from the top to bottom the place is simply a seething cauldron of jealousies and hatreds; there is no loyalty or decency anywhere about it, there is no place in it where a man counted for anything against a dollar". The owners make the workers do too much work. They fire workers without warning. There were few laws to protect the workers. The owners could do what they wanted. The workers had to work in bad conditions. The book does not say this, but the workers were tired and sick. They had no help. There were unions, but they did not help the workers. The workers were treated very badly. They could not leave. Sinclair says that the workers were like slaves, "Here is a population, low-class and mostly foreign, hanging always on the verge of starvation and dependent for its opportunities of life upon the whim of men every bit as brutal and unscrupulous as the old-time slave drivers; under such circumstances, immorality is exactly as inevitable, and as prevalent, as it is under the system of chattel slavery."

Many writers use words to make the reader feel a certain way about things. Some ways are better than others. F. Scott Fitzgerald uses many ways in his book, *The Great Gatsby*. He often uses words that do not usual go together to make a feeling. He also uses symbols to make feelings. Fitzgerald uses many colors, like gold, green, white/gray, and red/pink, as symbols. In *The Great Gatsby*, Fitzgerald makes these colors mean things and then uses them to make readers remember a feeling about something important.

Fitzgerald uses white/gray to mean uniformity. White is a bit nicer and more high class. Gray is older and faded. He shows this early in the book by always using these colors. Daisy and Jordan always wear white. Nick wears white to Gatsby's party. Tom wears a white shirt when he meets Myrtle. Catherine is very white. The only time people are not wearing white is when Nick is at Gatsby's party. There are many bright colors there. Fitzgerald uses white and gray to show common things. Nick goes to work down “white” streets. People at Gatsby's party have “gray” names on Nick's list. Catherine’s apartment is white. He also uses white and gray for common people and places. Jordan and Daisy had a white childhood. There are gray cars and gray land. The Italian child is gray. The dog-seller is an old gray man.

After Fitzgerald uses white/gray a lot, he uses them to show that something is not important. He does this with Daisy. After not using white/gray for a while, Fitzgerald describes Daisy in a white car. Readers start to see Daisy as less of a person and more like something that Gatsby wants. He does this more with Daisy. Her fur collar is gray. She wears white before Tom and Gatsby talk.

San Diego have good farm ground. The weather is warm and sunny. Farmers grow many things here. They grow things like tomatoes, citrus fruits, and leafy greens. They also grow squash, broccoli, herbs, and fruit trees. Many people want food from farms that use no chemicals. There are many groups that help farms do this. 

Many farms give tours. People can visit the farm, walk, and look at birds. This is good for the land and people. 

Farming without chemicals is good for animals and plants. But it can be hard work. Farmers have to work more to keep pests away. Sometimes, they lose more food. 

The farm I looked at is in Potrero, California. It is near a big forest. The land is good for many plants and animals. Some animals are in danger. 

People have lived on this land for a long time. First, Native Americans lived there. Then, people raised cows and cut down trees. Now, a farmer wants to grow food in a good way. The farmer wants to help the land and make money.

Culture is strong in any talk. Culture is what a group of people say it is. Culture is not the same for everyone. Not all people in a group are the same. It is not good to say all people from a country are the same. For example, it is not fair to say all people from Russia are the same. Culture is important in talks. A talker must know about the culture of the other talker. The talker must know how the other talker sees things. When a talker meets a new culture, they see it from their own point of view. They may compare it to their own culture.

To know a new culture, a talker must learn about its history and beliefs. A talker should not try to change the culture. A talker must accept the culture. A talker must work with the culture. This is especially true in talks when one talker has less power.

Culture is not just about countries. Companies have their own cultures. Some companies work long hours. Other companies work less. A company’s culture can be seen in how people dress, how they talk, and how they hire people. Some companies like to help others. Other companies only help charities they choose.

American companies are different from each other. Companies in different parts of America are also different. This shows that there are many different cultures within America. Some cultures may look the same on the outside. But there is more to them.

Values are very important. They show why people act the way they do. If a culture values saving face, a talker will not shame their company. If a culture values hard work, a talker will not give up easily in a talk. 

A talker must learn about the other talker’s culture.

The fool say in his heart, ‘There is no God.’ This saying come from Psalm 14 in the Bible. It is the start of Saint Anselm’s talk about God. Saint Thomas Aquinas also believe this. Both men talk about God. We want to know who has the best argument. We start by saying that both men believe in the same God, the God of the Bible.

Anselm say we find God inside ourselves. We can not think of God not being. This mean God is real because we know it. We do not need proof from outside. This is called faith.

Aquinas say we can prove God with reason. We can see God in the world around us. He has five reasons for God’s existence. He say that if we see parts of a puzzle, we know there is a missing part.

Both men have good points. But neither one give us a full proof of God.

A prince was born in the fifth or sixth century BCE. He would one day be called Buddha. Buddha left the world and became enlightened. His teachings start Buddhism. The oldest form is called Theravada Buddhism.

Buddhism is about two thousand five hundred years old. It is different now than when Buddha lived. This can be seen in Sri Lanka. There is an annual water-cutting ceremony. Monks and people take part. It has some meaning, even though Buddha did not teach about it.

Theravada Buddhism has changed over time. This is from inside and outside forces. Some forces are good, some are bad.

We will use special words in this talk. "Inside" means something from inside Buddhism. "Outside" means something from outside Buddhism. "Bad" means something that hurts Buddhism. "Good" means something that does not hurt Buddhism.

First, we look at the basic parts of Theravada Buddhism. Buddhists find safety in the three gems: Buddha, Dhamma, and Sangha. The Dhamma is the Buddhist teaching. It is in three parts:

* Sutta Pitaka: Stories about Buddha.
* Vinaya Pitaka: Rules for monks.
* Abhidhamma Pitaka: Ideas about Buddhism.

Buddhism teaches that there is no soul (Anatta). Life has suffering (Dukkha). Everything changes (Anicca). To end suffering, you must end the cycle of birth and death (Sansara). To end Sansara, you must end desire (lobha), hatred (dosa), and delusion (moha).

The Vinaya Pitaka has rules. For people, there are five rules:

1. Do not kill.
2. Do not lie.
3. Do not steal.
4. Do not have sex wrongly.
5. Do not drink alcohol.


Monks have more rules. The most important idea is the four noble truths:

1. Life is suffering.
2. Suffering is caused by wanting things.
3. Suffering can end.
4. There is a way to end suffering.

The United States and Mexico some times had big fights. The fights went on for many years, from 1836 to 1893.  A big fight was the Mexican-American War. The United States won the war. The United States got new land.  Many small fights also happened.  These fights stopped before World War One.

The fights started because of differences. The Americans and Mexicans had different ideas about religion, culture, and how to live. They also wanted the same land. This is like many other countries that fight. Countries next to each other often have problems. The United States and Mexico are like this.

David M. Pletcher said that the United States had big problems with Mexico and Cuba. These countries are close to the United States. Other countries in Latin America had good relations with the United States.

Religion was a big problem.  Sally Frahm said that Americans did not like Catholics and kings a long time ago. This is like the Cold War. The United States and the Soviet Union fought because they had different ideas.  The United States and Mexico fought because of religion. The English and Spanish did not like each other. This made it hard for the United States and Mexico to be friends.

The United States and Mexico had many problems. They fought over land. Bandits from the United States went into Mexico. This was a big problem.

The fights stopped when Mexico needed help from the United States. The United States wanted to help Mexico, not fight it.

Fifteen years ago, I became sick. I did not know I was sick. I was a nurse. I liked helping people. I did not have a good childhood. My family was not safe. I thought, "I will always have a job. People get sick." So, I was a nurse.

But then I was sick. I was forty-six years old. I had no money. I could not work. I am still sick. I get money from the government. But I have nothing.

Every day is hard. I worry. I am not safe. I need help from my family and friends. When bad things happen, you need help.

Life has problems. We do not know what will happen. We need to plan. But we also need to help each other.

Some people say we need to be strong and do things alone. But our country was built by people who helped each other. They shared food and helped each other.

I have things to help me if there is a disaster. I have food, water, and tools. But I also help my neighbors. We look out for each other.

Why do living things change over time? Are there limits on how they change? In 1917, D’Arcy Thompson said that we still do not know how to describe even simple living things with math. This is still true today. More recently, math has been used to study how shells grow. Our study looks at how math and experiments can help us understand how shells change over time. We used pictures of shells to measure parts of them. Then, we used a computer program to make models of shells. These models show us the possible shapes of shells.

A shell is like a tube that twists around. The twists are called whorls. They go around a center line called the columella. The size of the whorls can change. A line between the whorls is called a suture. The biggest whorl is the last one. All the whorls except the last one are the spire. The top of the spire is the apex. The bottom is the base. The animal lives inside the shell through an opening called the aperture.

We can look at shells in different ways. We can look at the top, the bottom, the opening, or the side. The usual way to look at a shell is with the opening facing us and the top pointing up.

To count the whorls, we look at the top of the shell. We draw a line that divides the shell. Then we count the whorls on each side of the line.

Think of a shell as a series of openings that move through time and space. The animal builds the shell one opening at a time. We can track the path of the opening with measurements.

We can make a math model of this path. Then we can change the numbers in the model to see how the shell changes shape.

Indonesia’s baby and young child death rate stay the same for ten years.  Indonesia will reach many goals, like clean water and toilets. But, baby and mother health is not good enough. Indonesia needs to make the health system better. 

Indonesia has more births with a doctor or nurse. Seventy-two percent of births have help. But, some births have helpers who are not doctors. They can not help if there is a problem. Many babies die because of bleeding.  More babies need help when they have a sick stomach. 

Cesarean births are low in Indonesia. Only four percent of births are c-sections.  In cities, seven percent are c-sections. In the country, it is only two percent.  This means people in cities have better care. The poor have less care. They can not pay for care.

Indonesia needs to think about how to help more babies and mothers. Should they make special programs or make the whole health system better? Special programs are quick. But, they can take money from other parts of health care. They can also make too many programs. This is bad.

Victorian books are known for their close looks at small things and their focus on the rich people of the time. Two books that are called Victorian but are different are Oliver Twist and Wuthering Heights. Both books use mystery and strange things, which is not usual for books from that time. This helps the readers understand the characters better.

Here is a part from Oliver Twist:

“Many confusing ideas came into his mind. He felt like he was still walking between Sikes and Crackit, who were arguing loudly. He could hear their words. When he looked at himself, he was talking to them. Suddenly, he heard a gunshot. People shouted and cried. Lights flashed, and everything was loud and messy. Someone took him away quickly. During these strange thoughts, he felt a pain inside him. It was a bad pain that hurt him all the time.”

The two books use mystery a lot, often in dreams or dreamlike states. But the way they use it is different in each book. In Oliver Twist, these strange events show us what is going on inside Oliver. They show us his sadness and how he sees the world around him. When Oliver is shot, he remembers it again in chapter 28. It feels like a dream. He is trying to find help. The words show that Oliver has no control over what is happening. He is very sick. The shooting makes him feel overwhelmed. He does not feel the pain of the shot anymore. He just feels a constant fear. The shooting shows that Oliver has no control. He cannot even try to stop it. It shows that he is losing hope. Old Fagin is making him feel hopeless and sad. It seems like Oliver would try to save himself if he wasn't so sad.

Here is a part from Wuthering Heights:

“The day went by. It felt like there was no day. It was gone as soon as it came. Then night came. It was a long night, but it also felt very short. It was long because of the scary silence. It was short because the hours went by so quickly.”

A few years ago, I work in a after school program. I help young children. I was good at English and reading. One boy, Adrian, had problems reading. He was in third or fourth grade. He did not read well. Some letters he knew, some he did not. This was strange. Adrian spoke good English. His mother came to the program. She only spoke Spanish. I spoke a little Spanish. We talked. Then I knew the problem. Adrian knew how to read, but he did not know the English letters well. I do not know if this helped him, but I hope he is doing better.

I tell this story to talk about language problems in schools. It is not always easy to see the problem. Even a child who speaks English can have problems reading.  We all know this is a problem. What can we do? For Adrian, the answer was easy. I helped him with English letters and sounds. But for children who do not speak much English, the answer is harder. There is no one way to fix this. We need many things to help. We need dual language programs, immersion programs, tutors, and ESL classes. We need to use all of these things together.

The dual language system is a good idea. It is good for all children, not just children who speak Spanish.  Children in these programs learn well. Some people are afraid of this idea. They think it wastes money and that most children will not benefit. This is not true. If we use these programs more often, all children will benefit. How can we do this? We do not need all teachers to speak two languages. That is not possible. But we can have helpers who speak two languages.

We learn about the big world when we are young. Some people go to church. Other people go to temple. Some people think about it by them self. Many people believe what their parents teach them. Some people do not believe. They think there is no world beyond our own. Our ideas change. We learn more about the world. We all try to understand our place in the world.

My father and I sat on the porch. It rained hard. We smoked. He said his favorite bird is a cardinal. He looked at the rain. He looked sad. His clothes were big on him. His hair was thin. He did not look at me. I felt lonely. I was afraid. I did not want to talk about how much I would miss him. I hugged him. We sat in silence.

My father died in December. He was sick for a long time. The doctors said he would not live long. He died five days after my birthday. I did not want to see him die. I did not go to the hospital. I stayed home. I thought about how he lived. I did not want to watch him die.

No one called me to tell me he was gone.

The Gothic story is old and new. Ian Watt says this in his book, *The Rise of the Gothic Novel*. Some say Gothic stories are not good. Others say they are great. Some say they are too strange. The first Gothic story is *The Castle of Otranto* by Horace Walpole. Walpole used old ideas and new ideas to make a new kind of story.

Walpole used old ways of telling stories on stage. He also used new ways of writing about nature. He called this a "Gothic Story." Gothic stories often use ideas from old stories, buildings, and customs. Even when *The Castle of Otranto* was new, the word "Gothic" meant many things. It meant old and not modern. People thought it was not as good as new things.

Gothic stories are a mix of old and new. They are old stories but told in a new way. This is why Gothic stories are still read today.

One important idea in Gothic stories is chivalry. Chivalry is about being a good knight.  Walpole wrote about chivalry in *The Castle of Otranto*. Chivalry means being brave, honest, and strong. Walpole thought people were not like this today.

Walpole wrote *The Castle of Otranto* during a time of trouble. There were problems in politics. People were fighting. Walpole was worried about the future. He might have thought that people were not as good as they used to be.

One character in the story is Frederic. He is a prince. He has been sad because of bad things. He is a brave knight. He is described as:

The story tells us that Frederic is like a good knight. He is brave, strong, and kind.

Supply chain control is the moves of jobs to send goods from when a customer orders them to the time the customer gets them. This move has many parts: making the goods, getting the things to make the goods, making the goods, and sending the goods to the customer. A person named Keith Oliver said the name "supply chain control" in 1982.  He said it is good to plan, do, and watch the steps to send goods to customers fast and well. 

There are six main parts to supply chain control: making the goods, getting the things to make the goods, having enough goods, choosing good places to make and send the goods, moving the goods, and sharing information. Business leaders use these parts to help customers.

Making the goods is the first step. It is the start of sending goods to customers. Leaders need to know what customers want. They look at what people are buying to know what products are popular. After they know what to make, they decide how many of each product to make. 

Leaders also choose the best place to make the goods. This place needs to make goods well and quickly. They must also make sure the goods are good enough to make the customer happy.  Leaders plan when to make the goods and how to keep the machines working. Making goods is very important. If one part is not done well, it can cost the company time and money.  For example, I worked at Wal-Mart and Target. Both stores have rules for everything they do. 

The second part is getting the things to make the goods. Leaders decide how to get the things needed to make the goods. Sometimes, they make the things themselves. Other times, they ask other companies to make them. Leaders do this to make things faster and cheaper.

Hitler live in Burma, sign say.

Ellen Page, star of Juno, stand alone on street. She hold piece of cardboard. Message on sign. Message is strange. Burma is country in Asia. Country have bad leaders. Leaders are mean. In 2007, people in Burma protest. Monks lead the protest. Monks wear yellow robes. This is called the Saffron Revolution. 

People want change. Government say no. Government fight people. Many people are hurt.

This is not new. Bad leaders hurt people. Many years ago, Roman leaders say they are gods. Japanese emperors also say they are gods. 

Bad things happen in China, Rwanda, and Germany. People protest for rights. Leaders hurt people.

Duke Ellington make good music. He play piano good. He lead his band for many years. He write music for his band. 

His music is good because he know how to make each player sound good. He make music that is new and interesting. He use all the sounds of his band. 

One example is his music, Creole Love Call.  He use voice like an instrument. He make the voice sound smooth and then rough.  He use different players to make the music interesting.

Another example is Hot and Bothered. He use trumpet and voice in this song. The trumpet and voice sound good together.

Ellington is a great musician. He make good music that people still like today.

She always want some thing. This want not go away. It start when she was about 14 years old. It still there when she was 17.  She want a person, not a thing.  But she not like any boys. Some boys want her. They try to talk to her. She not like them. She think about this. She want to know why this happen. She think about this for many years, but she not find an answer. She live her life and ask herself about this want.

Her home is usually calm. Her parents are good people. They not fight. They not fight with her much. The only time they fight is when she want to be free. She is different from her parents. She is fun and like by people. 

Today is not a calm day. She walk around her house. She want to be happy. She hear a small scream from the kitchen. It is her mother's voice. She run to the kitchen. "Mom! What wrong?" Her mother is on the floor. She say, "Ow!" She hurt. Her daughter say, "Mom, I take you to the hospital." Her mother say, "I need a ride." Her daughter help her mother to the car. She is strong. She can help her mother.

The hospital smell like medicine and sickness. But she not think about this. She want to help her mother. She take her mother to the doctor. The doctor look at her mother. Her daughter is worried. Her mother fall off a chair. She try to reach a vase.

This study look at if eating a “Mediterranean Diet” (Med diet) help people. The Med diet has many fruits, vegetables, and fish. It has little meat. The study use a score to show how well people follow the Med diet. People with a high score eat more like the Med diet.

The study find that people who eat like the Med diet have less heart disease. They also have less stroke.

This study look at 74,886 women. The women were nurses. The women did not have heart disease or diabetes.  

The nurses answer questions about what they eat. This help the study team know how well they follow the Med diet. The nurses answer these questions many times over 20 years.

The study look at things like how much the women smoke and if they take medicine. This help the study team make sure the results are correct.

The study find that women who eat more like the Med diet have less heart disease and stroke.

In two thousand seven, America had a big money problem. People lost jobs. Many houses had no buyers. Many big companies had no money. This problem is still here. We must ask: How did this happen? How can we stop it?

The problem was made by people who made money decisions that were not good. They made banks give out money to people who could not pay it back. The banks gave out money for houses that were too expensive. These banks gave money to Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac. These companies took the money and made more loans. When people could not pay back their loans, the banks had no money. This made the money problem even bigger.

The problem started in nineteen ninety nine. President Clinton wanted to be president again. He wanted more people to buy houses. So, he made it easy for banks to give out loans. A man named Steven Holmes wrote about this in the newspaper. He said that this could be a big problem later.

Many things made the problem worse. People bought houses with loans that changed price. This made the houses more expensive. Too many people had too much money in houses. When the price of houses went down, many people lost money. Five big banks had a lot of money in houses. They lost a lot of money.

Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac had a lot of money in houses too. The government had to help them.

Exposition is hard. It is the part of a story where you tell the reader things.  Exposition can make readers tired. It is like when a person talks too much.

Good writers do not tell too much.  They show the reader what is happening.  They use words to make images in the reader's mind.

For example, if a story tells the reader that a woman loves her husband, the writer can show this.  The writer can describe how the woman looks at her husband. The writer can describe what the woman says to her husband. 

If a story tells the reader that a man is sad, the writer can show this.  The writer can describe how the man walks. The writer can describe what the man says.

Good writers make the reader feel things. They make the reader care about the characters.

I see two news report from Columbus, Ohio. The first report was from NBC 4. It was live this morning (August 13, 2011). The first story was about a man in Ashley, Ohio. He hurt his wife. They did not say her name, but his name was Shad Hostettler. They showed his picture. He looked bad. They talked about the story for two minutes. They said he hurt his wife many times. He was arrested. I think they talked about the story for the right amount of time.
The second story was about a shooting. Travis Buyers was 18. He was hurt badly. He was in Sharon Woods. No one was arrested. The police were looking. This story was short. I think this was because he was a black man. I see this often. Black people are not talked about much when they are hurt. If a white person is hurt, the news talks a lot about it.
The next story was about a hole in a helicopter. Someone shot at the helicopter. They said it was a small bullet from a gun. Crime-Stoppers are offering money for information.
The next story was about rain this weekend. The news said it would be hot this weekend. The story was short. They wanted people to watch more.
There was a story about a robbery. A black man robbed a store. He was tall and heavy. They talked a lot about his skin color.
The last story was about a man named Rene Rodriguez. He was a drug dealer. He sold drugs from Texas to Ohio. The news said he was in prison for a long time. They said 300 months.  They also said he was Hispanic.

Brother have a strong bond. This bond is very strong. It has many feelings. It has love, pride, jealousy, and bad things. Brothers know each other better than anyone. They see themself when they look at their brother.

When things are bad, the true bond shows. This bond can be good or bad. The feelings are very strong. They have a big cost.

To know the brother bond, we must know the results. When a brother looks in his brother's eyes, he sees themself. He sees themself as they really are, not how others see them. Their actions show their true character.

"The Scarlet Ibis" shows this bond. Two brothers have strong feelings. They go on a trip that fails. Disappointment and pride fight in the end. Only one brother lives.

The story tells us about Doodle, the younger brother. We also see the story from the older brother's point of view. He has many complex feelings. His feelings change how he acts.

The older brother feels pride. From the start, he wants a brother who can do many things. He wants to teach him to run, jump, and climb. He wants a brother to race with and play with. But Doodle is weak. He has a bad heart. He can't do these things.

The older brother is angry. He thinks about hurting Doodle. But then Doodle smiles. The older brother feels love. He wants to protect Doodle.

The human brain is a big and clever system. It works with information like a computer. But the brain is much more than just a computer.

Long ago, people said the brain was like a wax tablet. Later, they said it was like paper. Now, people say it is like a computer. But these are just ways to help us understand the brain.

We learn things with our senses. We see, hear, touch, smell, and taste. Our senses send signals to the brain. The brain uses these signals to understand the world.

The brain works in two ways. First, it looks at small parts of information. For example, it looks at the color and shape of an object. Second, it uses what it already knows to understand new information.

For example, if you see a box, the brain looks at the color and shape. But it also knows what a box is. So, it can understand that it is a box quickly.

The brain is also good at paying attention. It can choose what to focus on. You see many things when you look around. But your brain pays attention to the most important things. 

The brain also stores information. There are different types of memory. Short-term memory is like a scratch pad. It holds information for a short time. Long-term memory is like a library. It holds information for a long time.

Scientists are still learning about how the brain works. There are many different theories. One theory is that the brain stores information in a network of connections. This network is like a map.

Aldous Huxley looks at the danger of new technology and money power. He shows this in the book *Brave New World*.  People in this world love being part of a group more than being alone. They want to be happy all the time. The people are like pieces in a game. A leader, the World Controller, tells them what to think.

If we look at this book with the ideas of Karl Marx, we see that Huxley is worried about these new systems. Words like "same" and "things become things" show that Huxley thinks these new systems are bad.

Huxley shows how money power is bad.  People in the lower classes do not know how money really works. They only think about getting things for themselves. This is because the people in charge control what they think.  The people in *Brave New World* do not have their own ideas. They are told to buy and spend money. The World Controller makes them do this.  

In this world, the people in charge control everything. The lower classes do not know they are being controlled. They think what the people in charge tell them is good. The people in charge know they are controlling things, but they do not do anything to stop it.

The people in *Brave New World* do not have real relationships. They are not interesting people. Maybe Huxley is saying that technology and money power make people forget who they are. They do not love or feel strong emotions. They only talk about looks.

The people in this world are happy with their place in society. They follow the rules. This shows how money power can control people.

I am a student at University Park. I have been here for two and a half years. Many students have trouble getting around campus. My first year, I lived in an East Halls dorm. This is far from the center of campus. Going to classes in places like Willard building could take twenty-five minutes by foot. The weather is often bad here.

An older student told me that the East Halls were far from the rest of the school. There was empty land between them. Now, there are new sports fields, buildings, and apartments. Campus is growing. It is harder to get around.

What is the best way to move around campus? Many students use bicycles. But the campus needs to be better for bikes.

I talked to a friend who rides a bike. He said, “Bikes are great. It is the best way to get around.” Bikes are good for your health and they are fast.

I live off campus now. The smart thing I did was buy a bike. My classes are in Thomas building. It is a long walk. But I can ride my bike in five minutes.

Pollock Road is the best way to go. But it is not always easy to ride there. Walking is good too. But I am busy. If I did not have a bike, I would have to walk. That would take a lot of time.
